/div></div></div></div> <span class="open-flyout"> <span class="visually-hidden">Open Flyout</span> </span></div></div> </header> <main role="main"> <a id="main-content" tabindex="-1"></a><div class="row g-0"><div class="col-12 layout-content"><div class="region region-content"><div data-drupal-messages-fallback class="hidden"></div><div id="block-northmarq-mainpagecontent" class="block block-system block-system-main-block"> <article id="landing-page-northmarq-home" class="node node--type-landing-page node--view-mode-full"><div class="node__content"><div class="section-container-fluid background-image-detail-tr-and-bl section-container-extended layout layout--onecol" id="layout-page-header"><div class="layout__region layout__region--content"><div class="block block-northmarq-micronode block-northmarq-micronode-blockhomepage-hero"><h1 class="visually-hidden">Nationwide Commercial Real Estate Services with Northmarq</h1><div id="homepage-hero-nationwide-commercial-real-estate-services-with-northmarq" class="node node--type-homepage-hero homepage-hero"><div data-duration=5000 class="slick-slider"><div class="homepage-hero__slide"><div data-nid="6706" class="is-first paragraph paragraph--type--featured-content paragraph--view-mode--default" id="featured-content-nationwide-commercial-real-estate-services-with-northmarq-slides"><div class="slide-homepage"><div class="slide-homepage__media"> <article class="media media--type-video media--view-mode-hero"><div class="field field--name-field-media-file field--type-file field--label-visually_hidden"><div class="field__label visually-hidden">Video file</div><div class="field__item"><video preload="none" loop="loop" muted="muted" width="1200" height="600" playsinline="true" webkit-playsinline="true"> <source src="/sites/default/files/2026-02/NM_Website-Hero_02-26_MarketSnapshot_Final.mp4" type="video/mp4" /> </video></div></div> </article></div><div class="container"><div class="slide-homepage__body"><h2 class="eyebrow"> Research &amp; Insights</h2><h3 class="title h1"> Just Released: Q4 2025 MarketSnapshot Reports</h3><div class="description"> Browse our quarterly market reports for data and commercial real estate trends across the single- and multi-tenant sectors of office, industrial and retail.</div><div class="ctas"> <a href="/trends-insights/research-library/marketsnapshot" title="Read more about MarketSnapshot"> View Reports </a></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="homepage-hero__slide"><div data-nid="371136" id="featured-content-nationwide-commercial-real-estate-services-with-northmarq-slides" class="paragraph paragraph--type--featured-content paragraph--view-mode--default"><div class="slide-homepage"><div class="slide-homepage__media"> <article class="media media--type-image media--view-mode-hero"><div class="field field--name-field-media-image field--type-image field--label-visually_hidden"><div class="field__label visually-hidden">Image</div><div class="field__item"> <picture> <source srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/30x13_full/public/images/NM_Website-Hero_02-26_Rent-Roll-Jay-Parsons_3_3840.jpg.webp?itok=kF8ybDpH 1x" media="only screen and (min-width: 61em)" type="image/webp" width="1440" height="624"/> <source srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/30_13_half/public/images/NM_Website-Hero_02-26_Rent-Roll-Jay-Parsons_3_3840.jpg.webp?itok=EdQRkNBS 1x" media="only screen and (min-width: 38.125em)" type="image/webp" width="720" height="312"/> <source srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/30_13_third/public/images/NM_Website-Hero_02-26_Rent-Roll-Jay-Parsons_3_3840.jpg.webp?itok=MauqFjIy 1x" media="only screen and (min-width: 16.5em)" type="image/webp" width="540" height="234"/> <img loading="eager" fetchpriority="low" width="1440" height="624" src="/sites/default/files/styles/30x13_full/public/images/NM_Website-Hero_02-26_Rent-Roll-Jay-Parsons_3_3840.jpg.webp?itok=kF8ybDpH" alt="Jay Parsons and Jeff Weidell headshots on blue background for the Rent Roll Podcast" /> </picture></div></div> </article></div><div class="container"><div class="slide-homepage__body"><h2 class="eyebrow"> Executive Insights</h2><h3 class="title h1"> Navigating Today’s Multifamily Debt Market</h3><div class="description"> Podcast host Jay Parsons and Northmarq’s CEO Jeff Weidell break down the evolution of multifamily lending, what’s driving capital flows and what regulatory changes could mean for future housing production.</div><div class="ctas"> <a href="/news/general-news/northmarq-ceo-jeff-weidell-featured-rent-roll-podcast-jay-parsons" title="Read more about Northmarq CEO Jeff Weidell featured on The Rent Roll Podcast with Jay Parsons"> Listen to the Podcast </a></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="homepage-hero__slide"><div data-nid="367621" id="featured-content-nationwide-commercial-real-estate-services-with-northmarq-slides" class="paragraph paragraph--type--featured-content paragraph--view-mode--default"><div class="slide-homepage"><div class="slide-homepage__media"> <article class="media media--type-image media--view-mode-hero"><div class="field field--name-field-media-image field--type-image field--label-visually_hidden"><div class="field__label visually-hidden">Image</div><div class="field__item"> <picture> <source srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/30x13_full/public/images/Bud-Cauley-Hero-Image-01_2026%20%281%29.jpg.webp?itok=R2M0JCgz 1x" media="only screen and (min-width: 61em)" type="image/webp" width="1440" height="624"/> <source srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/30_13_half/public/images/Bud-Cauley-Hero-Image-01_2026%20%281%29.jpg.webp?itok=7EO6rAQs 1x" media="only screen and (min-width: 38.125em)" type="image/webp" width="720" height="312"/> <source srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/30_13_third/public/images/Bud-Cauley-Hero-Image-01_2026%20%281%29.jpg.webp?itok=kl6L-uGc 1x" media="only screen and (min-width: 16.5em)" type="image/webp" width="540" height="234"/> <img loading="eager" fetchpriority="low" width="1440" height="624" src="/sites/default/files/styles/30x13_full/public/images/Bud-Cauley-Hero-Image-01_2026%20%281%29.jpg.webp?itok=R2M0JCgz" alt="Bud Cauley Swinging golf club wearing a Northmarq hat" /> </picture></div></div> </article></div><div class="container"><div class="slide-homepage__body"><h2 class="eyebrow"> PGA Tour Sponsorship</h2><h3 class="title h1"> Northmarq Announces Partnership with PGA Golfer</h3><div class="description"> Northmarq’s partnership with golfer Bud Cauley focuses on the role that preparation and readiness play in long-term performance, whether on the course or in business.</div><div class="ctas"> <a href="/news/press/pga-tour-golfer-bud-cauley-and-northmarq-announce-brand-partnership" title="Read more about PGA TOUR golfer Bud Cauley and Northmarq announce brand partnership"> Learn about Bud Cauley </a></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="homepage-hero__slide"><div class="slide-homepage"><div class="slide-homepage__media"> <article class="media media--type-image media--view-mode-hero"><div class="field field--name-field-media-image field--type-image field--label-visually_hidden"><div class="field__label visually-hidden">Image</div><div class="field__item"> <picture> <source srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/30x13_full/public/images/Open-Positions-Hero-Image-01_2026.jpg.webp?itok=x-U11wjN 1x" media="only screen and (min-width: 61em)" type="image/webp" width="1440" height="624"/> <source srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/30_13_half/public/images/Open-Positions-Hero-Image-01_2026.jpg.webp?itok=6pyAjzGp 1x" media="only screen and (min-width: 38.125em)" type="image/webp" width="720" height="312"/> <source srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/30_13_third/public/images/Open-Positions-Hero-Image-01_2026.jpg.webp?itok=1DYECwas 1x" media="only screen and (min-width: 16.5em)" type="image/webp" width="540" height="234"/> <img loading="eager" fetchpriority="low" width="1440" height="624" src="/sites/default/files/styles/30x13_full/public/images/Open-Positions-Hero-Image-01_2026.jpg.webp?itok=x-U11wjN" alt="Man with beard shaking hands looking for an open position at northmarq" /> </picture></div></div> </article></div><div class="container"><div class="slide-homepage__body"><h2 class="eyebrow"> Commercial Real Estate Careers</h2><h3 class="title h1"> Invested in You</h3><div class="description"> We prioritize hiring, training and retaining the most talented people in the commercial real estate industry. See how our inclusive company culture promotes collaboration, hard work, innovation and growth.</div><div class="ctas"> <a href="https://www.northmarq.com/careers/open-positions">Search open positions</a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="section-container-fluid section-container-extended layout layout--onecol" id="layout-"><div class="layout__region layout__region--content"><div class="views-element-container block block-views block-views-blocklisting-search-property-search-panel-form"><div><div class="view view-listing-search view-id-listing_search view-display-id-property_search_panel_form js-view-dom-id-7805a189f3cef7028f0c66597a2caabaf602a05ceaf18dedb4823d49a42f7949" id="property_search_panel_form"><div class="inner-container"><h2>Search Property Listings</h2><div class="view-filters"><form class="views-exposed-form bef-exposed-form northmarq-bef-exposed-form" data-drupal-selector="views-exposed-form-listing-search-property-search-panel-form" action="/properties" method="get" id="views-exposed-form-listing-search-property-search-panel-form" accept-charset="UTF-8"><div class="form--inline clearfix"><div class="js-form-item form-item js-form-type-select form-type-select js-form-item-property-type form-item-property-type"> <label for="edit-property-type--2">Property Types</label> <select class="northmarq-select-form-element northmarq-select-property_type form-select" data-drupal-selector="edit-property-type" multiple="multiple" name="property_type[]" id="edit-property-type--