<div class="field field--name-field-image field--type-entity-reference field--label-hidden field__item"> <img loading="lazy" src="/sites/default/files/styles/4x3_third/public/images/KC-MultifamilyConcessions-Feb2026.jpg.webp?itok=gjF2izDz" width="513" height="385" alt="Aerial View of Sunny Modern Apartment Complex with Landscaped Lawn" class="image-style-_x3-third" /></div></div><div class="node__category">Knowledge Center</div><div class="node__body"><h3 class="node__title"><span class="field field--name-title field--type-string field--label-hidden">What are multifamily concessions and how do they impact value and refinancing?</span></h3><div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden field__item"> Multifamily concessions explained: how free rent and incentives affect net effective rent, property value and refinancing outcomes for operators.</div><div class="field field--name-field-date field--type-datetime field--label-hidden field__item"><time datetime="2026-02-25T12:00:00Z" class="datetime">February 25, 2026</time></div></div></div> </a> </article></div></div><div class="views-view-responsive-grid__item"><div class="views-view-responsive-grid__item-inner"><article id="blog-post-dallas-fort-worth-multifamily-sales-volume-strengthens-to-close-2025" class="node node--type-blog-post node--view-mode-card"> <a href="/insights/insights/dallas-fort-worth-multifamily-sales-volume-strengthens-close-2025" aria-label="Dallas-Fort Worth multifamily sales volume strengthens to close 2025" rel="bookmark"><div class="node__content"><div class="node__media"><div class="field field--name-field-image field--type-entity-reference field--label-hidden field__item"> <img loading="lazy" src="/sites/default/files/styles/4x3_third/public/images/Dallas.jpg.webp?itok=DPnYodOe" width="513" height="385" alt="Skyline image of Dallas" class="image-style-_x3-third" /></div></div><div class="node__category">Insights</div><div class="node__body"><h3 class="node__title"><span class="field field--name-title field--type-string field--label-hidden">Dallas-Fort Worth multifamily sales volume strengthens to close 2025</span></h3><div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden field__item"> The Dallas-Fort Worth Metroplex accounted for 8% of the total net absorption in the country in 2025 and positioned for improvement.</div><div class="field field--name-field-date field--type-datetime field--label-hidden field__item"><time datetime="2026-02-25T12:00:00Z" class="datetime">February 25, 2026</time></div></div></div> </a> </article></div></div></div></div><div class="more-link"><a href="/research-insights">View all insights</a></div></div></div></div></div> </section> <section id="section2" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tab2" class="tabs-panel js-tabs-panel" tabindex="0"><div class="accordion-trigger js-accordion-trigger" aria-controls="section2" aria-expanded="true" tabindex="0">Transactions</div><div class="content" aria-hidden="false"><div class="field__item field__item-label-hidden"><div class="views-element-container"><div class="view view-combo view-id-combo view-display-id-transactions_cards js-view-dom-id-cb02c7288271450259534f50e3392c958bb68a92769d5a280fafb182648df54c"><div class="view-content"><div class="views-view-responsive-grid views-view-responsive-grid--horizontal" style="--views-responsive-grid--column-count:3;--views-responsive-grid--cell-min-width:320px;--views-responsive-grid--layout-gap:24px;"><div class="views-view-responsive-grid__item"><div class="views-view-responsive-grid__item-inner"><article id="transaction-bronx-multi-tenant-storefront-retail" class="node node--type-transaction node--view-mode-card"> <a href="/transactions/bronx-multi-tenant-storefront-retail-debt-permanent-loan-fixed-2026-03" aria-label="Bronx Multi-Tenant Storefront Retail" rel="bookmark"><div class="node__content"><div class="node__media"><div cl